# ============================================================
# Notes for travel mode:
# ============================================================
# - Change country code when traveling to comply with local regulations
# - Use strong password for travel WiFi
# - All traffic will go through VPN tunnel to home or Oracle
# - Consider lowering txpower in hotels to avoid interference
